Reasoning: The paper deals with the design of linear precoders and decoders for multiuser MIMO FBMC-OQAM modulations in the presence of strong channel frequency selectivity. This involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SI), networked systems (cs.NI), and multimedia (cs.MM).
